:

1. *Uostalom*, moramo se pomiriti sa činjenicom da je vreme brzo prolazno. (Anyway, we have to reconcile ourselves to the fact that time passes quickly.)
2. Nisam imao vremena da se zadržim, *uostalom* nisam ni hteo. (I didn't have the time to stay, anyway I didn't want to.)
3. *Uostalom*, ja sam već rekao svoje mišljenje. (After all, I have already expressed my opinion.)
4. *Uostalom*, to je ono što ja mislim u vezi sa ovim. (In any case, that is what I think about this.)
5. *Uostalom*, nije u pitanju samo to. (In any case, it is not just about that.)